---
const { variant = 'hoa' } = Astro.props;
const isRealty = variant === 'realty';
const isRental = variant === 'rental';
---
<section class="tw-section tw-section-cream" id="about">
  <div class="tw-container tw-mission-grid">
    <div class="tw-mission-image" style={isRental ? 'align-self:stretch' : ''}>
      <img src="/assets/hero-mission.jpg" alt={isRealty ? 'Tidewater Realty agents with a client' : 'Family-owned community in front of their home'} style={isRental ? 'height:100%;aspect-ratio:unset' : ''} />
      <div class="tw-mission-image-overlay">
        <p class="tw-mission-image-overlay-quote">&ldquo;Still family-owned. Still independent. Still here.&rdquo;</p>
        <div class="tw-mission-image-overlay-meta">Stanley &amp; Marc Greenberg</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tw-mission-copy">
      {isRental ? (
        <>
          <div class="tw-eyebrow">Tidewater Rental Management</div>
          <h2 class="tw-section-title">Family-owned.<br /><em>For landlords who can&rsquo;t be there.</em></h2>
          <p class="tw-section-lede" style="margin-bottom:16px">
            For over 35 years, Tidewater has managed rental properties across Maryland and coastal Delaware. We started with the same landlords who trusted us with their communities &mdash; and built a rental operation to the same standard. No national franchise. No rotating portfolio managers.
          </p>
          <p class="tw-section-lede">
            Whether you&rsquo;re deployed, out of state, or just done dealing with tenant calls yourself &mdash; our rental team runs the property. You get the portal, the statements, and the peace of mind.
          </p>
          <div class="tw-stats" style="gap:16px">
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num" style="font-size:1.5rem">35+</div><div class="tw-stat-label" style="font-size:9px">Years Rental Mgmt</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num" style="font-size:1.5rem">400+</div><div class="tw-stat-label" style="font-size:9px">Units Managed</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num" style="font-size:1.5rem">MD/DE</div><div class="tw-stat-label" style="font-size:9px">Licensed</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num" style="font-size:1.5rem">2</div><div class="tw-stat-label" style="font-size:9px">Generations</div></div>
          </div>
        </>
      ) : isRealty ? (
        <>
          <div class="tw-eyebrow">Tidewater Realty Group</div>
          <h2 class="tw-section-title">Family-owned brokerage.<br /><em>Investment-minded agents.</em></h2>
          <p class="tw-section-lede" style="margin-bottom:16px">
            When Stanley Greenberg founded Tidewater in 1989, property management and real estate were inseparable disciplines. Today, Tidewater Realty Group extends that same family-owned approach to buying, selling, and investing &mdash; with the full-service advantage of in-house management and maintenance behind every transaction.
          </p>
          <p class="tw-section-lede">
            Our agents know these properties from the inside out. They&rsquo;ve managed them, inspected them, and tracked their rental income. That&rsquo;s an advantage you won&rsquo;t find at a national brokerage.
          </p>
          <div class="tw-stats">
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num">35+</div><div class="tw-stat-label">Years in MD Market</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num">MD + DE</div><div class="tw-stat-label">Licensed Footprint</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num">In-house</div><div class="tw-stat-label">Mgmt &amp; Maintenance</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num">2</div><div class="tw-stat-label">Generations Family-Owned</div></div>
          </div>
        </>
      ) : (
        <>
          <div class="tw-eyebrow">Who We Are</div>
          <h2 class="tw-section-title">More than management.<br /><em>Your trusted community resource.</em></h2>
          <p class="tw-section-lede" style="margin-bottom:16px">
            Stanley Greenberg founded Tidewater in 1989. His son Marc &mdash; CMCA, AMS, PCAM &mdash; helped grow the company into a regional, full-service operation while keeping it family-owned. As regional competitors are acquired by national firms and private equity, we&rsquo;ve stayed independent on purpose.
          </p>
          <p class="tw-section-lede">
            The way that translates: open-door ownership, accessible managers, and the kind of decisions only people who answer to their own neighborhood make.
          </p>
          <div class="tw-stats">
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num">35+</div><div class="tw-stat-label">Years Independent</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num">400+</div><div class="tw-stat-label">Communities</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num">~75</div><div class="tw-stat-label">In-house Team</div></div>
            <div class="tw-stat"><div class="tw-stat-num">2</div><div class="tw-stat-label">Generations Family-Owned</div></div>
          </div>
        </>
      )}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
